baton that is designed

00:16:14.830 --> 00:16:17.910
out of all the ya's being
put together, right?

00:16:17.910 --> 00:16:21.980
So the ya gets thrown around
between different performers.

00:16:21.980 --> 00:16:24.440
So you're kind of going
ya, ha, ya, he, ha, ha,

00:16:24.440 --> 00:16:28.980
being thrown around two different
performers, and your flute part,

00:16:28.980 --> 00:16:33.790
