by Sinclair Arum [Assumed Spelling]

00:17:15.240 --> 00:17:18.700
and rocks music in a heterophonic
style, which became very,

00:17:18.700 --> 00:17:21.780
very interested -- people in
the West became very interested

00:17:21.780 --> 00:17:24.190
