then that became a kind of metaphor

00:17:33.370 --> 00:17:36.430
for organizing for political
life in many philosophies

00:17:36.430 --> 00:17:38.360
and political philosophies to
follow, which is interesting,

00:17:38.360 --> 00:17:39.660
all the way up until today.

00:17:39.660 --> 00:17:42.500
