01:23:05.170 --> 01:23:10.640
notice that the left-hand thumb
is the one that is charged

01:23:10.640 --> 01:23:14.320
with two manuals, while the right
hand has only got one manual.

01:23:14.320 --> 01:23:17.840 position:56%
This is a reversal of the
psychology of asymmetry in the West,

01:23:17.840 --> 01:23:19.140
that we're all righthanded

01:23:19.140 --> 01:23:21.490
and our technology is designed
around righthandedness.

01:23:21.490 --> 01:23:23.920
This is in some sense
constraining the left hand

01:23:23.920 --> 01:23:26.210
as being the dominant hand, okay?

01:23:26.210 --> 01:23:29.420
That's the first thing to take into
