01:25:17.350 --> 01:25:20.420
Okay, et cetera, okay?

01:25:20.420 --> 01:25:23.870
So what happens is this player is
going down, up, down, down, down,

01:25:23.870 --> 01:25:26.190
up, down, down, up -- and this
one up, down, up, down, down.

01:25:26.190 --> 01:25:33.290
But the ear is picking up that
