01:29:48.300 --> 01:29:53.820
So a pattern that is fixed has
managed to dislocate itself

01:29:53.820 --> 01:29:58.010
or be set adrift from the
meter and has shifted over

01:29:58.010 --> 01:30:05.610
or metrically modulated to a place
elsewhere in that pattern, right?

01:30:05.610 --> 01:30:07.230
But not in a way that
you might expect.

01:30:07.230 --> 01:30:09.310
This isn't I'm going to start
