01:30:09.310 --> 01:30:12.350
to follow me like six beats
later with the same music.

01:30:12.350 --> 01:30:15.860
But rather I'm going to simply
change the smallest detail

01:30:15.860 --> 01:30:17.850
in the way I'm moving my form.

01:30:17.850 --> 01:30:24.490
And suddenly it throws this new
voice into alignment, misalignment.

01:30:24.490 --> 01:30:27.240
In other words, it's not just
the transformation of pattern

01:30:27.240 --> 01:30:29.380
that happens, but it's
transformation

01:30:29.380 --> 01:30:32.560
that recoups similar to it, right?

01:30:32.560 --> 01:30:35.210
A similar pattern reappears
as a phantom pattern,

01:30:35.210 --> 01:30:38.360
but dislocated from
